[{"id":"2ce62084d38f45c3a2e6dfe9c7bc08189d0e876ea39602383fa8d9ed34d08535","title":"Пилотный подкаст первого сезона","summary":"\n\nДобрый день уважаемые сл...","description":"<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/loose.dtd\">\n<html><body>\n<p>Добрый день уважаемые слушатели. Представляем новый выпуск подкаста RWpod. В этом выпуске:</p> <h2 id=\"ruby\">Ruby</h2> <ul> <li><a href=\"http://weblog.rubyonrails.org/2013/1/28/Rails-3-0-20-and-2-3-16-have-been-released/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Уязвимость в рельсах 3.0.x и 2.3.x</a></li> <li><a href=\"http://blog.plataformatec.com.br/2013/01/security-announcement-devise-v2-2-3-v2-1-3-v2-0-5-and-v1-5-3-released/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Уязвимость в devise (не касается PostgreSQL or SQLite3)</a></li> <li><a href=\"http://venturebeat.com/2013/01/30/rubygems-org-hacked-interrupting-heroku-services-and-putting-millions-of-sites-using-rails-at-risk/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Rubygems взломан</a></li> <li>Методы ускорения вашего Rails приложения (использование кеширования): <a href=\"http://blog.craz8.com/articles/2013/1/7/how-do-i-make-my-rails-app-faster\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">тут</a> и <a href=\"http://blog.craz8.com/articles/2013/1/17/seven-advanced-rails-fragment-cache-techniques\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">тут</a>\n</li> <li><a href=\"http://blog.phusion.nl/2013/01/24/phusion-passenger-4-0-beta-2-syscall-failure-simulation-framework-focus-on-stability/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Phusion Passenger 4.0 beta 2</a></li> <li><a href=\"http://georgi.github.com/audite/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Аудио библиотека для Ruby</a></li> <li><a href=\"http://solnic.eu/2013/01/23/mutation-testing-with-mutant.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Тестирование с помощью Mutanta</a></li> <li><a href=\"http://rubytune.com/cheat\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Спредшит консольных команд</a></li> </ul> <h2 id=\"javascript\">JavaScript</h2> <ul> <li><a href=\"https://github.com/kjbekkelund/writings/blob/master/published/understanding-backbone.md\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Мигрируем с JQuery на Backbone.js</a></li> <li><a href=\"http://engineering.twitter.com/2013/01/introducing-flight-web-application.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Flight.js - new framework from Twitter!</a></li> <li><a href=\"http://www.jsdb.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">База JS библиотек</a></li> <li><a href=\"http://hoejs.schettino72.net/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Hoe.js</a></li> <li><a href=\"http://goldfirestudios.com/blog/104/howler.js-Modern-Web-Audio-Javascript-Library\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Аудио библиотека</a></li> </ul> <p></p>\n</body></html>\n","date":"Sat, 02 Feb 2013 00:00:00 +0200","human_date":"02.02.2013","link":"https://www.rwpod.com/posts/2013/02/02/podcast-01-00.html","main_img":"https://www.rwpod.com/images/logo200.png","audio_url":"https://mp3.rwpod-assets.com/podcasts/01/0100.mp3","audio_file_size":31446228,"audio_type":"audio/mpeg","audio_duration":"00:13:06"}]

